Few improvements in the Analytics
* If you select Today. You will see all the task from before
  if they are not yet finished. They will be in red.
  And if all the task for today are finished, you will also
  see in blue the task from later days.
* The time passed string was changed to "days gone" and
  "days left" for better way to calculate your ways through
  the days. I will add more features to it in future.
